No. 370,

Misc.

Order of Railroad Telegraphers et al. v. Duffy et al., U. S. Court of Appeals Judges, et al. Alex Elson, Lester P. Schoene, Brainerd Currie and Philip B. Kurland for petitioners. Solicitor General Rankin for the Judges of the United States Court of Appeals for the Seventh Circuit, and Carl McGowan for the Chicago & North Western Railway Co., respondents.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of mandamus denied.
